trans-unit.source: The type of an element in the controlled sequence.
trans-unit.target: 受控序列中的元素的类型。

trans-unit.source: Supports simple iteration over any STL/CLR object that implements the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.IList`1" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 支持对实现 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.IList`1" /> 接口的任何 STL/CLR 对象执行简单迭代。

trans-unit.source: The first node in the container over which to iterate.
trans-unit.target: 要对其进行循环访问的容器中的第一个节点。

trans-unit.source: Allocates and initializes a new <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 分配并初始化新的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置集合中的当前元素。

trans-unit.source: The current element in the collection.
Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 释放或重置 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> 对象使用的非托管资源。

trans-unit.source: Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 释放或重置 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> 对象使用的非托管资源。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to dispose of managed objects; <see langword="false" /> to dispose of unmanaged objects.
trans-unit.target: 释放托管对象为 <see langword="true" />；释放非托管对象为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 释放或重置 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.ListEnumerator`1" /> 对象使用的非托管资源。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数前移到集合中的下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果枚举数已成功地推进到下一个元素，则为 <see langword="true" />；如果枚举数传递到集合的末尾，则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数设置为其初始位置，该位置位于集合中第一个元素之前。
